<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFD342DEEFC6FFAC7" author="De Candolle, A. P." box="[681,966,1274,1301]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" refId="ref8849" refString="De Candolle, A. P. (1828) Melastomaceae. In: De Candolle, A. P. (Ed.) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive enumeratio contracta ordinum, generum, specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarum, juxta methodi naturalis normas digesta. Vol. 3. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Parisiis [Paris], pp. 99 - 202. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1828">De Candolle (1828: 123)</bibRefCitation>
