<subSubSection id="84BB6540FFEDFFAEFF152C73FEFCF9AF" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="CC1E36CBFFEDFFAEFF152C73FEFCF9AF" blockId="4.[136,1452,1382,1660]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFF152C73FF58FA53" bold="true" box="[136,241,1382,1408]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Notes:—</emphasis>
When describing 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFE212C73FC56FA53" authority=", Humboldt &amp; Bonpland (1812)" authorityName=", Humboldt &amp; Bonpland" authorityYear="1812" box="[444,1023,1382,1409]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Rhexia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leptophylla">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFE212C73FD3BFA53" box="[444,658,1382,1408]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Rhexia leptophylla</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFD3E2C73FC56FA53" author="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A." box="[675,1023,1382,1408]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="57 - 68" refId="ref9375" refString="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A. (1812) Voyage de Humboldt et Bonpland. Monographie des Melastomacees. Rhexies. Libreria Graeco-Latino-Germanica, Paris, pp. 57 - 68. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 16027" type="book chapter" year="1812">Humboldt &amp; Bonpland (1812)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
indicated only the type location, but not the original material. When searching for the original material with that name, we found 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFB272C9EFA0DFA77" box="[1210,1444,1418,1445]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEDFFAEFB272C9EFB67FA76" box="[1210,1230,1419,1445]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15406" name="Harvard University - Arnold Arboretum" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="Herbarium">A</collectionCode>
. 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEDFFAEFB4F2C9EFB4BFA76" box="[1234,1250,1419,1445]" country="South Africa" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14647" name="University of the Witwatersrand" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="Herbarium">J</collectionCode>
. 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEDFFAEFB7B2C9EFB53FA76" box="[1254,1274,1419,1445]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15406" name="Harvard University - Arnold Arboretum" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="Herbarium">A</collectionCode>
. Bonpland s.n.
</emphasis>
, at 
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEDFFAEFF392CBAFF1AFA1A" box="[164,179,1455,1481]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
(
<collectionCode id="AAB0AE0EFFEDFFAEFF5E2CBBFF7AFA1A" box="[195,211,1454,1481]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
00136388), where the collections examined by the authors of the species were found (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFB382CBBFF6AFA3F" author="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A." pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="137 - 158" refId="ref9493" refString="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A. (1823) Voyage de Humboldt et Bonpland. Monographie des Melastomacees. Rhexies. Libreria Graeco-Latino-Germanica, Paris, pp. I - II + pp. 137 - 158. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 16027" type="book chapter" year="1823">Humboldt &amp; Bonpland 1823</bibRefCitation>
, see Preface), with the same location indicated in the protologue (
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFC252CC7FAACFA3F" author="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A." box="[952,1285,1490,1516]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="57 - 68" refId="ref9375" refString="Humboldt, F. W. H. A. &amp; Bonpland, A. J. A. (1812) Voyage de Humboldt et Bonpland. Monographie des Melastomacees. Rhexies. Libreria Graeco-Latino-Germanica, Paris, pp. 57 - 68. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 16027" type="book chapter" year="1812">Humboldt &amp; Bonpland 1812</bibRefCitation>
). Additionally, only this collection was analyzed in treatments after 
<taxonomicName id="0BA14D48FFEDFFAEFD642CE3FC79F9C3" authorityName=", Humboldt &amp; Bonpland" authorityYear="1812" box="[761,976,1526,1552]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Rhexia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="leptophylla">
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFD642CE3FC79F9C3" box="[761,976,1526,1552]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">Rhexia leptophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was published (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFB522CE2FA0EF9C3" author="De Candolle, A. P." box="[1231,1447,1526,1553]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" refId="ref8849" refString="De Candolle, A. P. (1828) Melastomaceae. In: De Candolle, A. P. (Ed.) Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis, sive enumeratio contracta ordinum, generum, specierumque plantarum huc usque cognitarum, juxta methodi naturalis normas digesta. Vol. 3. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Parisiis [Paris], pp. 99 - 202. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 286" type="book" year="1828">De Candolle 1828</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFF152F0FFE83F9E6" author="Naudin, C. V." box="[136,298,1562,1589]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" pagination="25 - 39" refId="ref10001" refString="Naudin, C. V. (1850 a) Melastomacearum qu ӕ in Mus ӕo Parisiensi continentur. Monographic ӕ descriptionis et secundum affinitates distributionis tentamen. (sequentia.). Annales des Sciences Naturelles, Botanique, ser. 3, 13: 25 - 39." type="journal article" year="1850">Naudin 1850a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="A8304B3AFFEDFFAEFEAB2F0FFE4EF9E6" author="Cogniaux, A." box="[310,487,1562,1589]" pageId="4" pageNumber="251" refId="ref8702" refString="Cogniaux, A. (1885) Melastomaceae. Tribus II. Tibouchineae Baill. In: Martius, C. F. P. &amp; Eichler, A. G. (Eds.) Flora brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas. Vol. 14. Frid. Fleischer, Monachii et Lipsiae [Munich &amp; Leipzig], pp. 205 - 510. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="book" year="1885">Cogniaux 1885</bibRefCitation>
). Thus, we conclude that 
<emphasis id="FED5EAD9FFEDFFAEFC952F0EFC46F9E7" box="[776,1007,1562,1589]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="251">
